{
  "stem": "25591.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So what the-- what the Holocaust has done to me, it made me a human rights activist.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it took me some time to-- to physically recover and then I was sent back to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And shortly thereafter, I successfully escaped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Made my way to a-- a Wallenberg protected house, number 25 Saint Stephen Park, very near the bank of the Danube where my aunt and uncle had an apartment.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But of course by this time, it was not their apartment-- 25 people, 30 people lived in a place that plus for two people or three people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I became part of this group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not-- it's very difficult for me to distinguish between what I know now and what I knew then.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I want to be very cautious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first thing I want to say is that although I worked with Wallenberg, and I was one of the young men who helped his operation, I was a young kid, one of hundreds, so I was in no sense a collaborator of his.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- I was a tiny, tiny cog in a vast apparatus.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my principal virtue, I think was two-fold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One, that I looked very Aryan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I looked as-- I looked like a Hitlerjugend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was blue eyed, blond, tall with very Nordic features, so I could be used as a messenger.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was sent out to collect-- my-- my most intense memories relate to collecting medications for people, various medications.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The one person I remember most was a middle-aged man who had the regular asthma attacks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'd never seen an asthma attack before this gentleman came into my life or I came into his life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he had to lie down on the floor and was gasping for air.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
